{
  "stem": "9943.5",
  "chunk_idx": 5,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.8,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And I suggested to her that maybe she'll go with me so then she will have work, and I will not be going-- will not be going there alone.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And she will be the helper.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "So she said she has-- she has to discuss it with a friend of hers that she's with them, and she agreed.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So-- so I went with her, myself, and her friend, and his friend to that kolhoz.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So we arrived to that kolhoz, myself and three people with me, assuming that they were going to accompany us, two of us, to this village.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "It took us three or four days there to-- we were waiting for the chairman of the kolhoz.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "In the meantime, we don't live any place.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "We just sit in this office, sit in a sitting position, sleep like the same-- the same kind of a way, and-- [PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] and wait.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So came [INAUDIBLE] that handled that kolhoz, [INAUDIBLE] is his name.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And he said he doesn't need a doctor because they have doctor, doctor's office was just opposite their kolhoz.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So I said to him, well, sign to me on a piece of paper that you-- that you don't honor that-- that-- that they send me here.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And I'll go back to-- to the-- to the office, and they will send me somewhere else.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So he was afraid to sign because they are terribly afraid of such things there in the Soviet Union.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "We got the piece of paper, so-- so he agreed.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And so this way we remained in the kolhoz, and these two young men left to-- to town.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And we-- me and [?",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Cooker ?] is her name.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Her real name was Rachel Alpert.-- Alpert, A-L-P-E-R-T.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "That's '41.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "'41.",
      "word_count": 1
    }
  ],
